\PYG{k}{2.} User sees ...

\PYG{g+gu}{\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{} Key Interactions}
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }List of interactive elements on THIS page (not children).

\PYG{g+gu}{\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{} Preconditions}
